Dice :
	done

Board :
	150 cases par 100 cases
	Opposite corners
	Obstacles :
		Outboard or collision = elimated

Round :
	Turn alternates between players
	Need to activate a ship before using it
	Activation :
		One activation per ship per turn
		Activation is irreversible.
		3 phases :
			order:
				pp = 0 => initial values;
				1pp speed = 1d6 block
				1pp shield = 1 shield point
				1pp weapon = 1d6 weapon
				repair if immobile (1d6), 6 = full repair
			movement:
				virage gratuit si immobile
				speed = max block
				inerty = nb case mini avant de rester immobile
				si immobile, ok moins inerty
				si inerty ok, ok virage
				si percute, fin du tour
					degats si inerty = 0 => chaque vaisseau = degat points coque autre vaisseau / reduit par bouclier
			tir :
				charges 0. si pp, 1d6 par pp. parfois charge > 0 par defaut
				portee courte, moyenne, max
				zone effet
				see tir pour plus d'infos

			shoot
	New round after all activated

Ships :
	name
	size
	sprite
	hp (5)
	pp (10 to 15)
	speed (20 to 10)
	inerty !!!!!
	Shield
	Weapons
